    dc:creator "Rosa, Paolo; Wei, Na-Sen; Notton, David; Xu, Zai-Fu" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Revision of the Oriental genus Holophris Mocsáry, 1890 and description of the genus Leptopareia Rosa & Xu, gen. nov. (Hymenoptera, Chrysididae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053817>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053819>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053821>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053823>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053827>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053825>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053829>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053831>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053833>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053835>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053837> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053817>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Mesopleuron and metapleuron, lateral view. A. Omalus aeneus (Fabricius); B. Holophris marginella (Mocsáry); C. Leptopareia borneana (Cameron)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053817/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053819>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Fore wing venation. A. Leptopareia borneana (Cameron); B. Holophris thailandica sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053819/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053821>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Head, lateral view. A. Leptopareia borneana (Cameron); B. Holophris taiwana (Tsuneki). Arrow pointing to subgenal carina." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053821/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053823>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Holophris marginella (Mocsáry), ♀, Hainan, Bawangling. A. Habitus, lateral view; B. Head, frontal view. C. Head, pronotum and mesoscutum, dorsal view; D. Mesosoma, dorsal view; E. Metasoma, dorsal view; F. T 3, posterior view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053823/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053827>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Holophris thailandica sp. nov., ♀, holotype. A. Habitus, lateral view; B. Head, frontal view; C. Head and mesosoma, dorsal view; D. Mesosoma, dorsal view; E. Metasoma, lateral view; F. T 3, posterior view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053827/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053825>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Holophris taiwana (Tsuneki), ♀, Hainan, Diaoluoshan. A. Habitus, lateral view; B. Head, frontal view; C. Head, pronotum and mesoscutum, dorsal view; D. Mesosoma, dorsal view; E. Metasoma, dorsal view; F. T 3, posterior view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053825/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053829>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Leptopareia borneana (Cameron), ♀, lectotype. A. Habitus, lateral view; B. Head, frontal view; C. Head and mesosoma, dorsal view; D. Metasoma, dorsal view; E. Head, dorsal view; F. T 3, dorsal view. (© The Trustees of the Natural History Museum, London)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053829/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053831>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Leptopareia luzonensis sp. nov., ♀, holotype. A. Habitus, lateral view; B. Head, frontal view; C. Mesosoma, dorsal view; D. Metasoma, dorsal view; E. Metasoma, lateral view; F. T 3, posterior view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053831/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053833>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Leptopareia purpurea (Smith), ♀, holotype. A. Habitus, lateral view; B. Head, frontal view; C. Mesosoma, dorsal view; D. Metasoma, dorsal view; E. Metasoma, ventral view; F. T 3, dorsal view. (Photos courtesy of Dr. James Hogan)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053833/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053835>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Leptopareia abyssinica (Mocsáry), ♀, holotype, Harrar, Ethiopia (HNHM). A. Habitus, lateral view; B. Head, frontal view; C. Mesosoma, dorsal view; D. Metasoma, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053835/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053837>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Leptopareia congoensis (du Buysson), ♀, holotype of its synonym L. bayonii (Mantero, 1910) from Busso Busoga, Uganda (MSNG). A. Head, mesosoma, and T 1, lateral view; B. Head, frontal view; C. Mesosoma and T 1, dorsal view; D. T 3, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053837/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

